name: MyNewLife
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my new life
des:
Have you ever dreamed of being a sailor? How about a professional athlete?

Now you can be all those thing and more by asking Alexa for a new life. Each time you ask Alexa to launch "My New Life" you will automatically receive a random age, career, and description of your new life. 

It's easy, fun and totally free. See what your new life holds in store for you!
